87
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,660
just like today.

88
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:27,060
Your kindness to me,

89
00:07:29,580 --> 00:07:30,900
I've never forgotten.

90
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:34,820
You always ask if I love you.

91
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,220
In truth,

92
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:39,260
I've always asked myself

93
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,220
