96
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,820
It wasn't because I liked them.

97
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,540
I just didn't want you

98
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:54,660
feeling bored at home,

99
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:57,020
